{"tid":2046398,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國歐盟商會主席：中國宣傳部門成功將中國變成歐洲人需要面對嘅問題","createTime":"2020-06-01T11:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T12:46:35.000Z","uid":138409,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"adb0e2f815e8102960de054568b90af6f81b34c7","tid":2046398,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"之前開左個post<br />\n講歐盟唔支持制裁中國<br />\n搞到大家都屌歐盟<br />\n<br />\n但係我地應該做嘅嘢<br />\n係盡力向歐洲剖析利弊遊說佢哋支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歐盟都唔係鐵板一塊<br />\n&lsquo;It is a very sad story to see how the propaganda ministry - within four to six weeks - managed to turn China into a problem for Europeans, and how China&rsquo;s standing in Europe is eroding by the day.&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=120857942967449&amp;id=104528267933750\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D120857942967449%26id%3D104528267933750&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8x5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=8b9d92ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=120857942967449&amp;id=104528267933750</a><br />\n<br />\n中國歐盟商會主席Joerg Wuttke在這篇訪談中說，&ldquo;歐洲一直對中國抱有同情，特別是在1月份中國陷入疫情的時候，歐洲人被武漢人民在陽臺上唱歌的場景所感動。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;然而，這種好感在2月中下旬的時候突然掉轉了。當時，中國給歐洲，特別是意大利，捐贈醫療設備，然後大吹了一通。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;真正惹惱我們的是，當1月份歐洲人民和歐洲公司給中國捐錢、捐設備的時候，中國政府跟我們說：低調，不要聲張。所以我們就沒說什麼。然而到了2月，中國突然開始對任何捐給歐洲的口罩都大書特書。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">&ldquo;除此之外，我們還在面對着&lsquo;戰狼&rsquo;外交官們。他們就在我們的首都&mdash;&mdash;斯德哥爾摩、巴黎、布拉格，等等。&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;非常令人難過的是，宣傳部門在4-6周的時間裏，就成功把中國變成了歐洲人需要面對的問題，並且中國在歐洲的地位還在一天天被這樣侵蝕。&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\nJoerg Wuttke在中國待了30年，在這篇訪談中他還談了對中國政府的不少看法，值得一讀：<a href=\"https://www.chinadebate.com/china-macro-&hellip;/joerg-wuttke-may20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinadebate.com%2Fchina-macro-%E2%80%A6%2Fjoerg-wuttke-may20&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8x5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=1be7bf2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinadebate.com/china-macro-&hellip;/joerg-wuttke-may20</a>"},{"pid":"d2fd984c40dd7dc3909249432f39497fa355e4b6","tid":2046398,"uid":224882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"講得咁搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e24f9a836314eaa512b38e126d497ecc3321c97","tid":2046398,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9e9652a02bc4c529e10deda5e7ef1cd5b2a7c2d","tid":2046398,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"81ff4549b13d3334a8d3e5f1c442cd43b65e82b1","tid":2046398,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:06:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c90b0b61f32e08896c98fb626560085baca4e31b","tid":2046398,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:43:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"460512a6e066d71902c99f9cf09ca55e2971937c","tid":2046398,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"push"}]}